caption.text: Hello my friends! 💗 I hope you are having a beautiful day 💓 I’d like to give you a high paw 🐾 and tell you how grateful I am to be your friend! Thank you for making time to read my posts and to see my face! There aren’t enough words to say how special I feel about this connection between us! I’d like also to ask you if you like my advices and know someone that may like or need my words, tag this person in my posts so I can reach more and more souls and accomplish my dream: to be a speaker of love to the world ♥️ Thanks for being my friend and showing me how amazing humans can be and transform through love! Remember my friend: we are all here to grow and evolve and that’s why we need each other. Be the messager of kindness and love wherever you go. It will never be too much! caption.text: “Anchored Mermaid”🧜🏻‍♀️ It was a month ago now that I bruised (possibly fractured) my tailbone in Maui. What a conflict of interest. This is how I spent my time in paradise...however it turns out I was also there to get proposed to by @danger_havok , which absolutely helped with distracting me from the pain. I’m still recovering from the blow to my booty, but the memories are priceless and I miss being there so much. Take me back.
